---
---
<!-- FOUNDING CAPACITY SECTION -->
<section id="capacity" class="relative overflow-hidden border-b border-line">
  <div class="grid-bg absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-40" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="accent-glow absolute -top-32 -left-40 w-[520px] h-[520px] z-0" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-5xl px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="card relative overflow-hidden p-7 sm:p-10 lg:p-12">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-[auto_1fr] gap-8 lg:gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="lg:pt-2">
          <div class="relative inline-flex flex-col items-start gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-accent/40 bg-accent/10 px-6 py-5 sm:px-8 sm:py-6 shadow-[0_20px_50px_-20px_rgba(255,107,26,0.45)]">
            <span class="font-display text-[0.7rem] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Now Accepting</span>
            <span class="font-display font-bold text-[3.5rem] sm:text-[4.2rem] lg:text-[5rem] leading-none text-text">
              <span class="text-accent">3</span>
            </span>
            <span class="font-display text-[0.78rem] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-text-soft">Founding Wizard Builds</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Limited Capacity</span>
          <h2 class="mt-4 text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.6rem] leading-[1.05] font-bold tracking-tight">
            Only 3 Founding Builds Are Open
          </h2>

          <p class="mt-5 text-text-soft text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed">
            Custom quote and booking systems take real strategy, copy, logic, and testing. We take a maximum of 3 active wizard builds at a time so each one gets the attention it needs.
          </p>

          <p class="mt-4 text-text-soft text-[1.02rem] leading-relaxed">
            The platform is already proven and running at Fitchin. Founding clients get a custom build based on the same core platform — at locked-in pricing — in exchange for an honest testimonial and permission to use the project as a case study.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-baseline gap-x-4 gap-y-2">
            <div>
              <div class="font-display text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-accent">Founding rate</div>
              <div class="font-display font-bold text-[1.6rem] text-text">$2,995 setup + $147/mo</div>
            </div>
            <div class="opacity-70">
              <div class="font-display text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-text-muted">Standard rate</div>
              <div class="font-display text-[1.1rem] text-text-muted line-through decoration-line-2">$3,995 setup + $197/mo</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="mt-5 text-text-soft text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed">
            Locked-in monthly rate stays put for as long as you stay subscribed and the scope stays the same.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-[0.82rem] font-display font-medium text-accent uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">
            <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
              <span class="absolute inset-0 rounded-full bg-accent animate-ping opacity-60"></span>
              <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-accent"></span>
            </span>
            Now accepting 3 founding Wizard clients
          </div>

          <div class="mt-7">
            <a href="#apply" class="btn-primary">
              Apply Before Founding Pricing Closes
              <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<!-- /FOUNDING CAPACITY SECTION -->
